Ak <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ullorianlanys.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Llorian Lanys</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Board Whore</span><br> <font color=#000033>(1/3/02 9:42:16 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.mindspring.com/~suretang/images/usf2.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: INT vs. CHA vs. AC vs. HP</span><hr size=1> If you are asking what people are doing now because of the new lessening of the cap in regards to gear, i can say that my thoughts havent changed much at all.<br>
